<h3>Split Button</h3>

<p>Note that you can also make a DropdownItem into a seperator by adding IsDivider="true" to the DropdownItem.</p>

<div class="docs-example">
    <BSDropdown>
        <BSButtonGroup>
            <BSButton Color="Color.Secondary">Action</BSButton>
            <BSDropdownToggle IsSplit="true" Color="Color.Secondary" />
            <BSDropdownMenu>
                <BSDropdownItem Href="#">Action</BSDropdownItem>
                <BSDropdownItem Href="#">Another Action</BSDropdownItem>
                <BSDropdownItem IsDivider="true" />
                <BSDropdownItem Href="#">Yet Another Action</BSDropdownItem>
            </BSDropdownMenu>
        </BSButtonGroup>
    </BSDropdown>
</div>
